entries.transmission_start: \#pcontrast3 Tactical computer: < \#pcontrast1 A large number of hyperspace signatures detected. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.title_d: Launch an attack on the Black Sun assault force moving into Yavin Space
entries.title: Yavin System: Intercept the Black Sun Assault
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: Travel here to intercept the Black Sun force
entries.quest_location_d: An area of Imperial control in the Yavin System
entries.quest_defendpoint_d: Stay at this position through the duration of the assault
entries.outofrange_failed: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 What are you hoping to accomplish out there?  This ambush was a horrible idea. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.outofrange: \#pcontrast3 Nav Computer: < \#pcontrast1 You are moving out of range for the ambush, return to the nav location. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.mission_complete: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 That is enough, whatever plans they had are pointless now.  Return to base. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Calculated entry point is here, move into position. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.first_attack: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 The hyperspace signatures are spiking, be ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile activity has ceased. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile craft detected on attack vector. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 Ok, this is the spot.  This will probably go down in history as the worst ambush ever, but stay focused and stay alive... we want those Black Sun destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
